I'm fine.

852
01:03:03.200 --> 01:03:05.820
Hey, let's go down to the hotel
for dinner tonight.

853
01:03:05.990 --> 01:03:07.780
- Really?
- Yeah.

854
01:03:07.950 --> 01:03:10.660
I gotta do something
to pull me out of my "Mexi-coma."

855
01:03:10.830 --> 01:03:13.410
Oh, honey, you made a little joke.

856
01:03:13.580 --> 01:03:15.500
